0.6
---

Add `sync` argument to be able to run bash in non-blocking form

0.5
---

Allow passing in of stderr

0.4
---

Introduce subprocess32 use if available for timeout use.
Removed support for python 3.2
Added support for python 3.5

0.3.1
-----

Fixed issue with getting the value of a stdout=None bash object.

0.3
---

Ability to override stdout to not go to a pipe.

0.2
---

Ability to pass in env overrides when running commands.

0.1
---

Ability to run and chain commands.
